    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p><strong>Rise and shine! Before you begin\u2026</strong></p><p>Skim through these steps and get all your equipment ready</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hot-honey-bacon-and-fried-egg-pancakes/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Take 1 tbsp per person of <strong>butter </strong>out of the fridge and set aside to soften</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>smoked streaky bacon</strong> to the pan and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hot-honey-bacon-and-fried-egg-pancakes/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>honey</strong> and<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>hot honey</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hot-honey-bacon-and-fried-egg-pancakes/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, crack your<strong> egg[s] </strong>into the pan</p><p>Tip: Give your egg a little shake before you crack for a perfectly centred yolk!</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hot-honey-bacon-and-fried-egg-pancakes/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>buttermilk</strong> <strong>pancakes</strong> to a plate and pop in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 30 secs on high or until warmed through</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hot-honey-bacon-and-fried-egg-pancakes/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once crisp, transfer the <strong>bacon</strong> to kitchen paper and reserve the pan</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hot-honey-bacon-and-fried-egg-pancakes/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>hot honey</strong> and the <strong>softened</strong> <strong>butter</strong> to the reserved pan and cook over a low heat for 1-2 min or until melted \u2013 this is your <strong>hot honey butter sauce</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/hot-honey-bacon-and-fried-egg-pancakes/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>buttermilk pancakes</strong> topped with a <strong>fried egg</strong>, some <strong>crispy bacon</strong> and the <strong>hot honey butter sauce</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
